mixin tokenRecipe(header)
  +tokenFigure

  if header != ""
    h2 #{header}
  h3 
    div.number 4 
    | Design and issue your own cryptocurrency

  p Create a tradeable digital token that can be used as a currency, a representation of an asset, a virtual share, a proof of membership or anything at all. These tokens use a standard coin API, so your contract will be automatically compatible with any wallet, other contract or exchange also using this standard. The total amount of tokens in circulation can be set to a simple fixed amount, or fluctuate based on any programmed ruleset.

